body: This tankoubon ranked number 4 in the 30 best-selling manga of the year in Toranoana and did not reach the number 1 position because it went on sale on December 24 ... that's how good this work is

Always appreciate a tankoubon from key. Something that's been on my mind is how key's art style hasn't evolved at all over the years. It was good to begin with, but it's rare to see 0 change. Most other top tier artists I can think of somewhat changed in the last 5 years or so, while key's been in it for at least 7 years.
